{"article_id":"OZ0dSzmMYbdhyuaO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has cancelled a summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong-un ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"blaming `` tremendous anger and open hostility '' from the North .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"it was possible a meeting could still take place","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"but warned North Korea against committing `` foolish '' acts .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The meeting would have discussed ways","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"of denuclearising the Korean peninsula ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"building on a historic North-South Korea summit in April .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"In a statement","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"released by the North 's central news agency ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Vice-Foreign Minister Kim Kye Gwan said","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"the country held Mr Trump 's efforts","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"to hold a summit","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"`` in high regards '' .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"`` We tell the United States once more","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that we are open to resolving problems at any time in any way , ''","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"But even before the US president 's announcement , doubts had emerged on both sides","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"about whether the talks would take place .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Mr Trump 's statement marks a fresh twist in the turbulent relationship between him and Mr Kim .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Last year saw the two exchange lurid insults and mutual threats of annihilation .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"This year though has seen warmer relations .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"In the build up to the meeting , as a goodwill gesture , North Korea released three Americans","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"it had in prison ..","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"North Korea had also dismantled tunnels at its only nuclear test site only hours before Mr Trump 's announcement .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"A senior administration official later gave more details about the summit 's cancellation ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"North Korea showed `` a profound lack of good faith '' in the run-up to the meeting .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"There were a series of `` broken promises '' from Pyongyang ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the official told reporters ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"including when the White House sent the deputy chief of staff to Singapore","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to meet North Korean diplomats ahead of the summit .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"`` The North Koreans did n't show up .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"They simply stood us up . ''","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"The official also said","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"President Trump had `` dictated every word '' of the letter to Kim Jong-un","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"after talking with South Korean President Moon Jae-in .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"The meeting","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"- in Singapore on 12 June -","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"would have been the first time","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"a sitting US president met a North Korean leader .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"The Trump administration insists","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that North Korea was not responding sufficiently in the summit preparations ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"raising doubts","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that the meeting would be able to achieve a positive outcome .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Prior to the thaw in relations between North and South Korea","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that began the process","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that led to the summit date ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"wild rhetoric was being exchanged between Pyongyang and Washington","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"raising serious fears of a renewed conflict on the Korean Peninsula .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Will North Korea now resume its long-range ballistic missile testing ?","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Will the war of words be renewed ?","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Or might there be a slim chance","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"of some kind of diplomatic process being maintained ?","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"And finally , can relations between North and South Korea be insulated in any way from the growing tensions between Pyongyang and Washington ?","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"he had been `` very much looking forward '' to meeting Mr Kim .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` Sadly ,","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"based on the tremendous anger and open hostility","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"displayed in your most recent statement ,","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"I feel","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"it is inappropriate , at this time , to have the long-planned meeting , ''","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Mr Trump said in a letter to Mr Kim .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"`` You talk about your nuclear capabilities ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"but ours are so massive and powerful","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that I pray to God","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"they will never have to be used , ''","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"But he called the meeting a `` missed opportunity '' ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` someday , I look very much forward to meeting you '' .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"In a later statement at the White House , Mr Trump said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"the step was a `` tremendous setback for North Korea and the world '' ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"the US military was `` ready","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"if necessary ''","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"to respond to any `` reckless '' act from North Korea .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Mr Trump was apparently responding to statements from North Korea","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"attacking his administration","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"and casting doubt over the meeting .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Earlier on Thursday , North Korean official Choe Son-hui dismissed remarks by US Vice-President Mike Pence","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"- who had said","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"North Korea `` may end like Libya '' -","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"as `` stupid '' .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Ms Choe ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"who has been involved in several diplomatic interactions with the US over the past decade ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"the North would not `` beg '' for dialogue","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and warned of a `` nuclear showdown ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"if diplomacy failed .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"A White House official","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"quoted by Reuters","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"described the comments about Mr Pence as the `` last straw '' .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"They stressed , however ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"there was a `` backdoor","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that 's open still '' .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"References to Libya have angered North Korea .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"There , former leader Colonel Gaddafi gave up his nuclear programme","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"only for him to be killed by Western-backed rebels a few years later .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"South Korean President Moon Jae-in said","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"he was `` very perplexed","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"and it is very regrettable","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"that the North Korea-US summit will not be held '' ,","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"the Yonhap agency reported .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"It was South Korean officials who first informed the US","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"that Mr Kim was prepared to discuss potential nuclear disarmament .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"In April , the leaders of both Koreas had a historic meeting at the border ,","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"promising to end hostilities and work towards a denuclearisation of the Korea peninsula .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"UN Secretary General Antonio Guterres said","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"the US and North Korea should not give up ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"`` nerves of steel '' were required .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"In the US , Republican Senator Tom Cotton praised President Trump","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"for `` seeing through Kim Jong-un 's fraud '' .","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"But Democratic Senator Brian Schatz said","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"the move was what happened `` when amateurs are combined with warmongers '' .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":214,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":152,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":120,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":117,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":133,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":122,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":121,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":127,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":124,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN